sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Orchestrator as LangGraph
    participant State as FinSightState
    participant Auditor as Auditor Agent
    participant Planner as Planner Agent
    participant Analytics as Analytics Agent
    participant Insights as Insights Agent
    participant Validation as Validation Agent
    participant Viz as Visualization Agent
    participant Report as Report Agent
    participant LLM as LLM Gateway

    User->>API: POST /api/v1/upload (CSV)
    API->>State: Initialize FinSightState
    API->>Orchestrator: Run Workflow
    
    Orchestrator->>Auditor: Execute Node
    Auditor->>LLM: Identify Domain & Profile
    LLM-->>Auditor: Return JSON Profile
    Auditor->>State: Update Dataset Profile
    
    Orchestrator->>Planner: Execute Node
    Planner->>State: Read Profile
    Planner->>LLM: Generate Analytical Roadmap
    LLM-->>Planner: Structured JSON Plan
    Planner->>State: Update Workflow Tracking
    
    Orchestrator->>Analytics: Execute Node
    Analytics->>State: Read Plan & Dataset
    Analytics->>Analytics: Compute KPIs & Stats
    Analytics->>State: Update Business Analytics
    
    Orchestrator->>Insights: Execute Node
    Insights->>State: Read Analytics
    Insights->>LLM: Generate Strategic Summary
    LLM-->>Insights: Executive Summary & Risks
    Insights->>State: Update AI Insights
    
    Orchestrator->>Validation: Execute Node
    Validation->>State: Read Insights & Dataset
    Validation->>LLM: Fact-Check Claims
    LLM-->>Validation: Hallucination Scores
    Validation->>State: Update Validation Results
    
    Orchestrator->>Viz: Execute Node
    Viz->>State: Read Analytics & Validation
    Viz->>Viz: Generate Matplotlib PNGs
    Viz->>State: Update Generated Charts
    
    Orchestrator->>Report: Execute Node
    Report->>State: Read All Graph Data
    Report->>Report: Build PDF, HTML Dashboard
    Report->>Report: Export JSON Traces
    Report->>Report: Zip Artifacts
    Report->>State: Update Exports Paths
    
    Orchestrator-->>API: Workflow Complete
    API-->>User: Return HTTP 200 (Result Payload)
